    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a secret agent</h2>Complete most diverse missions: keep away from robots and solve logic puzzles as a newly employed secret agent. Who is Mr Meal? What is he up to?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/0a3d1c07934453c289b79326459b31d2.poster.avif?t=1716630026\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/0a3d1c07934453c289b79326459b31d2.webm?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/0a3d1c07934453c289b79326459b31d2.mp4?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Live in the base</h2>Agency headquarters - this is where you live and prepare for your missions. Here you can meet other individuals and hear their stories. Explore and discover the secrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/f8c25cfe2195ccf19464d9d1e1e9285d.poster.avif?t=1716630026\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/f8c25cfe2195ccf19464d9d1e1e9285d.webm?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/f8c25cfe2195ccf19464d9d1e1e9285d.mp4?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the world</h2>Wander into three nearby towns. Check the sewers and find out what is hidden underground and in the mountains. And that mysterious abandoned town...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/6e2d1d2c04305b3cc41dd8b8acb4176c.poster.avif?t=1716630026\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/6e2d1d2c04305b3cc41dd8b8acb4176c.webm?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/6e2d1d2c04305b3cc41dd8b8acb4176c.mp4?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be a part of community</h2>Meeting people on your way will let you hear their stories and uncover the secrets. You can possibly cross paths with Mr Meals's staff.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/c0e0019ca447eca480d8574d2c1ad453.poster.avif?t=1716630026\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/c0e0019ca447eca480d8574d2c1ad453.webm?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/c0e0019ca447eca480d8574d2c1ad453.mp4?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be yourself</h2>Make doalogue choices. Collect outfits, and dress as you like.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/b77d0de54e87d8d5e4378cf249d4c0aa.poster.avif?t=1716630026\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/b77d0de54e87d8d5e4378cf249d4c0aa.webm?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834570/extras/b77d0de54e87d8d5e4378cf249d4c0aa.mp4?t=1716630026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is mostly based on dialogues and puzzle-arcade missions. There are also mini-games both as part of the main storyline and side activities.<br><br>-------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional information</h2>This game contains flashing images that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive disorders. Please take caution.",
